description: OverviewHigh Quality RJ45 550 Mhz Category 6 Cat6 Ethernet Patch CableBuilt For Superior Network Speed and Reliable ConnectivityThe Category 6 cable (Cat6) is the cable standard for Gigabit Ethernet and other network protocols. This cable supports up to 550 MHz and is suitable for 10Base-T, 100BASE-TX (Fast Ethernet), 1000BASE-T / 1000BASE-TX (Gigabit Ethernet) and 10GBASE-T (10-Gigabit Ethernet).GearIt Cat6 cables are made of 100% bare copper wire as opposed to copper clad aluminum (CCA) wire, therefore fully compliant with UL Code 444, which require pure bare copper wire in Cat6 communications cables. This high performance bulk cabling is perfect for your custom network installation projects.
